race.description: Ladbrokes Big Bets Copy Now Handicap (C3)
race.comment: DETRIMENTAL (1) has hit a purple patch of late with a win and four placings from his past five starts and will be rock-hard fit for this mile trip. Gets a bunch of weight off with the 3kg claim and should be right there at the business end. BACKSTAGE (9) got a well-deserved victory over this course and distance at the latest effort and will have taken some confidence from that win. Definite winning hope again. ZOU BIG BOY (7) is an honest commodity who has hit the top-five in all six outings this preparation. Top-three candidate. KADALL (2) gets Maloney on board from the low draw and shouldn't be underestimated. CARPACCIO (4) best of the rest in an open race to close out the card.
